PageInfo.Message:
From the Arts Support screen, you can now
register up to two <COL ffdc78>Custom Skill
Palettes</COL>.
<Palette switching method on the Arts Support
screen>
When registering skills on the Arts Support
screen,
you can switch palettes with 【<KC UI_X>】.

The two palettes you set can be switched at any
time.
<How to switch palettes under normal conditions>
[<KC CHANGE_SKILLSET>] long press
*Be careful during battle, as you will be
unprotected until the palette is switched.
